caption: Pretty little park in Marais district -- oasis of calm and quiet (and there's even a doggy play area).
Great park to let the kids play for a while. Football and basketball courts, playground, toilettes, etc

Small garden protected by condominium all around. You can walk and relax along the small paths, as well as sitting in one of the many benches or on the grass. In general very crowded with kids and elderly people taking a breath outside.
Great park and place you can do some activities

Friendly, open, safe and well-lit park.  I bought some lunch at a local supermarket and ate it here. There was no trash and otherwise clean of (human) waste.  Lots of benches!  A nice place to spend the afternoon in :)
Lively park with sports facilities, slides, a giant sandbox, and twisting paths cutting through urban herb gardens.
Lovely park but sadly the longest was closed when we visited. Fab artwork around the park. Lovely fountain, green areas and inner city tranquility.
Stopped by here on my way to visit Pere Lachaise cemetery.  Very beautiful park. Lots of shade and seating area. Dog friendly.
Beautiful park with a playground and a basketball court! Just didn't have a basketball to play with sadly
A beautiful hidden garden with circular paths you can get lost in.  The story of this place is quite sad though, it used to be a prison for minors in the 19th and 20th century.
Lovely playground for children
Nice little park. Good playground for 5-10 years kids
Very lively neighborhood yet so calm at night! Plus there’s a dog park☺️☺️
Very lovely garden with really nice flowers. Good place to have a picnic!
Quite a nice place with  a 5 vs 5 football field and a basketball field where anyone can play
Nice parck, green area, place for children, possible play basketball and soccer
This park is very nice, and a good bit of green in this part of the city.
Quaint, but some nice flowers for this time of year.
Big, great for kids. Nothing fancy about it. Clean. Forget toilets...
A normal little park.
Nice playground for small as well as medium kids.
It's a regular park where I also had a little pique-nique.
Its Nice cosy with beautiful fontaine.i go often !!
